
2.  Artifacts

	Create clumps of three artifacts

	Each clump has a ritual which may only be learned
	if one of the artifacts is possessed.

	Ritual requires all three artifacts.
	Perhaps also a special location.
	Special location might be guarded by a nasty monster.

	Creates another artifact, or a useful skill, or a powerful unit.

	Give each player an artifact when they start

	Scatter some artifacts as rewards.

	Perhaps combo of weapons necessary to defeat monster


	helm			+n defense
	shield			+n defense
	sword			+n attack
	dagger			+n attack
	spear			+n missile
	bow			+n missile
	staff			+n aura
	ring			+n aura
	amulet			never sick

	magic %s
	%s of {name list, darkness, power}
	old %s

	elfstone		passage to faery
	staff of the dead	passage to hades
	robe			speeded study
	locator crystal		locate up to n away
	scrying orb		scry up to n away

	attack / move X
		"Only one who holds Foo [xxx] will conquer Beast [yyy]"
		"Only one who holds Foo [xxx] may enter Place [yyy]"

	Level 1 artifact set:
		Create three artifacts A B C
		Create ritual skill S
		Research A B C yields S
		S if of form: take A B C to place L, use S
		USE S consumes A B C, yields level 2 artifact

	Level 2 artifact set:
		Create item
		"Only the holder of X may defeat Foo in Z"
		Give level 3 artifact to Foo

	Level 3 artifact:
		"Place [x] is only visible to one who holds [y]"
		"Go to [x].  Only you will be able to see Foo [y]."


